dct_description_sm: surveyed for the Proprietor Charles M. Weber by Richd. P. Hammond Bvt. Major 3d. Artillery.
2 bar scales on map, given in "feet" and "miles."
Ancillary map: Map of a portion of the valley of the San Joaquin, including Stockton and its environs (scale [approximately 1:260,000]).
